## Summary

ShowCart's hierarchical agent architecture provides:

✅ **Intelligent Routing** - Super agent delegates to specialists
✅ **Context Efficiency** - Isolated subagent contexts
✅ **User Transparency** - Full execution visible in UI
✅ **Specialization** - Each agent focuses on domain
✅ **Scalability** - Easy to add new subagents
✅ **Type Safety** - End-to-end TypeScript types
✅ **Cost Optimization** - Right model for each task

The pattern follows AI SDK best practices and enables complex multi-step workflows while maintaining clean, manageable code.
